{"tid":1186943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京提名曾偉雄競逐聯合國駐維也納辦公室總幹事","createTime":"2019-06-05T09:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T10:25:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9ee4d38c198c554482e2bc041d3a9ce7303ceb","tid":1186943,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T09:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1461119_1_L_20190605171647.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1461119_1_L_20190605171647.jpg&h=d11544cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（港台圖片）<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人耿爽表示，中國政府已經提名香港警務處前處長、國家禁毒委副主任曾偉雄，競逐聯合國駐維也納辦公室總幹事兼聯合國毒品和犯罪問題辦公室執行主任。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽稱，這是中方堅定維護多邊主義，支持聯合國工作的具體體現。中方願為推進打擊跨國有組織犯罪，開展國際禁毒合作做出更大的貢獻。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461119-20190605.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461119-20190605.htm&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKL0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=3e26ed22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461119-20190605.htm&h=a42466e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461119-20190605.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8ba086f1cfa6c37bd6e26c1bd06e67273b0a4f5d","tid":1186943,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T09:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/53296997_1930865253709539_8575134126108049408_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=86963fbda4db47344b7cb9174088b69d&amp;oe=5D8C2DEB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F53296997_1930865253709539_8575134126108049408_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D86963fbda4db47344b7cb9174088b69d%26oe%3D5D8C2DEB&